Dump Similar Places

Commands | Dump Similar Places

LONG FORMAT

Reads Twitter credentials directly from command line arguments.

java -jar TSAK.jar tsak -consumerKey=XXXXX -consumerSecret=XXXXX -accessToken=XXXXX -accessSecret=XXXXX dumpSimilarPlaces -lat 51.5072 -long 0.1275 -pname london -o places.txt

SHORT FORMAT

Reads Twitter credentials from tsak.properties file as pointed by TSAK_CONF ENV variable.

java -jar TSAK.jar tsak dumpSimilarPlaces -lat 51.5072 -long 0.1275 -pname london -o places.txt

Arguments:

XXXX:

Twitter APP and User Keys. Please refer to SETUP page to see how to generate these four keys.

-lat:

Latitude of the place, for which the result will be returned.

-long:

Longitude of the place, for which the result will be returned.

-pname:

Name of the place, for which the result will be returned.

-o:

Name of the output file to which the result will be dumped.

Description:

This command will dump all the similar place to the specified place, of which details are provided.
